Oh, hey.
Thinking of joining the vigilantes, are
you? Kidding, kidding!

rows.label: tlk41300022_03_msg0001
rows.name:
An Superbian acquaintance of mine
told me they're secretly manufacturing
some kind of artificial Blades.

rows.label: tlk41300022_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Apparently, they don't even need to
bond or anything like that? I don't
know if there's any truth in it...

rows.label: tlk41300022_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Wish I could get one to help me out
with the vigilantes. We're so short-
staffed right now...
